MADELYN ATTACK bumped at the start, vied between horses early, fell back and lacked the needed late response. MISS HIGH N MIGHTY bumped at the start, was in contention briefly, fell back and went evenly late. RAIN ATTACK broke slowly, was in close while racing outside, went five wide on the turn and had nothing left for the drive.
